function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.2.13') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.2.13!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.4.0') < 0) {
	err('You need at least PHP Version 7.4 to update to this version');
}

if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != 'af8cda48080401dafb5efa1ef06ba09fcfce9529') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'af8cda48080401dafb5efa1ef06ba09fcfce9529') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '67018b1a92a31506fcfe48f58942a007e5184e8c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'af8cda48080401dafb5efa1ef06ba09fcfce9529') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != '0910aacdf6b109e124e5f419132a4dcfbd17bd4c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '0910aacdf6b109e124e5f419132a4dcfbd17bd4c') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '11c75e1438fdf5b41b75c7564cae31b8ccd43a68') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '0910aacdf6b109e124e5f419132a4dcfbd17bd4c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('OiRuWzFdJywgJyRuWzJdJywgJzAnLCAnMScpO1xuIjsKCX0gZWxzZSB7CgkJLy8gSVNPIG9yIEpvaW50LUlTTy1JVFUtVCBPSUQgQ291bnRyaWVzICgxLjIgYW5kIDIuMTYpCgkJZWNobyAiSU5TRVJUIElOVE8gYGFzbjFpZGAgKG9pZCwgbmFtZSwgc3RhbmRhcmRp'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('emVkLCB3ZWxsX2tub3duKSBWQUxVRVMgKCdvaWQ6JG5bMV0nLCAnJG5bMl0nLCAnMCcsICcxJyk7XG4iOwoJCWVjaG8gIklOU0VSVCBJTlRPIGBpcmlgIChvaWQsIG5hbWUsIGxvbmdhcmMsIHdlbGxfa25vd24pIFZBTFVFUyAoJ29pZDokblsxXScsICciLnN0cnRv'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('dXBwZXIoJG5bMl0pLiInLCAnMCcsICcxJyk7XG4iOwoJfQp9CgplY2hvICJcbiI7CmVjaG8gJy0tIEdlbmVyYXRvciAiZ2VuZXJhdGVfd2VsbGtub3duX2NvdW50cnlfc3FsaXRlIiBjaGVja3N1bSAnLmRlY2hleChjcmMzMigkY2hlY2tfc3VtKSkuIlxuIjsK'));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite');
	writefile_9();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite') != '0e1cf98fda406601fa2de72794b2dd1c09189658') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite') !== '0e1cf98fda406601fa2de72794b2dd1c09189658') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite') !== '43180b8a20cafe2c6e088dcde056f6bb039eeebb') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_9();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite') !== '0e1cf98fda406601fa2de72794b2dd1c09189658') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_country_sqlite');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') != 'd141b6e96cf39bec8c0d2ae4c2431e77dff233c0') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== 'd141b6e96cf39bec8c0d2ae4c2431e77dff233c0') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== '8eff53d5c1259c05cae88f3d5467bed101d95be9') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== 'd141b6e96cf39bec8c0d2ae4c2431e77dff233c0') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('YXNuMSkgewoJCWVjaG8gIiRsaW5lX2FzbjFcbiI7Cgl9Cglmb3JlYWNoICgkZGF0YVsnaXJpJ10gYXMgJGxpbmVfaXJpKSB7CgkJZWNobyAiJGxpbmVfaXJpXG4iOwoJfQoJZm9yZWFjaCAoJGRhdGFbJ2NoZWNrc3VtJ10gYXMgJGNodW5rKSB7CgkJJGNoZWNrX3N1'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('bSAuPSAkY2h1bms7Cgl9CgllY2hvICJcbiI7Cn0KZWNobyAnLS0gR2VuZXJhdG9yICJnZW5lcmF0ZV93ZWxsa25vd25fb3RoZXJfZmlyZWJpcmQiIGNoZWNrc3VtICcuZGVjaGV4KGNyYzMyKCRjaGVja19zdW0pKS4iXG4iOwo='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	writefile_11();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') != '71564f5670b16a07f0a66b5468c66ba38f68d257') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') !== '71564f5670b16a07f0a66b5468c66ba38f68d257') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') !== '5e06618a2e59c0677d6971d53f58cf38c68a26b7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') !== '71564f5670b16a07f0a66b5468c66ba38f68d257') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	writefile_12();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') != '10897d903bddd1c2e53f189eb57a3e4bc27e1ed2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '10897d903bddd1c2e53f189eb57a3e4bc27e1ed2') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== 'a6766a0983dd21ca5045dc97760e3051938a46e0') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_12();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '10897d903bddd1c2e53f189eb57a3e4bc27e1ed2') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
		}
	}
}

	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') != 'c8d0cc2f00f4706c219639201cba739bd3cc9910') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== 'c8d0cc2f00f4706c219639201cba739bd3cc9910') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== '918f548d3a0f37d259ea45f65e1852c241317beb') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== 'c8d0cc2f00f4706c219639201cba739bd3cc9910') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	writefile_14();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') != '0b07e23def3d8ef2fa08f15fd27614010658a15c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') !== '0b07e23def3d8ef2fa08f15fd27614010658a15c') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') !== '8cf18a69814fe93772db43c58de19dcac4328ec5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') !== '0b07e23def3d8ef2fa08f15fd27614010658a15c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	writefile_15();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') != '0f60132851705a83bf38eb83176bf4c0088954a6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '0f60132851705a83bf38eb83176bf4c0088954a6') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '3a78b474c4cf80e46fc0c90d13f17a7c914ffd87') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '0f60132851705a83bf38eb83176bf4c0088954a6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite
function writefile_16() {
	$fp = @fopen('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite', 'w');
	if ($fp === false) {
		warn('File dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite cannot be written');

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') != '90641078dec2f2950830d6c36b62b0432ea9a615') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== '90641078dec2f2950830d6c36b62b0432ea9a615') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== 'a4eb408087bda0d99d785b38161670d438a6dbdb') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== '90641078dec2f2950830d6c36b62b0432ea9a615') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/vendor_update.sh')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/vendor_update.sh');
	writefile_17();
	if (!is_file('dev/vendor_update.sh')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/vendor_update.sh');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/vendor_update.sh') != 'a176f55c9f63277d0aa83f1f2dfef58848589ee9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/vendor_update.sh');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/vendor_update.sh', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/vendor_update.sh');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/vendor_update.sh') !== 'a176f55c9f63277d0aa83f1f2dfef58848589ee9') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/vendor_update.sh') !== '8cf252cd9367cfba5f800034dc2ce86bead066b5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/vendor_update.sh');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/vendor_update.sh');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/vendor_update.sh')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/vendor_update.sh', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_17();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/vendor_update.sh') !== 'a176f55c9f63277d0aa83f1f2dfef58848589ee9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/vendor_update.sh');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/config_values.md')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/config_values.md');
	writefile_18();
	if (!is_file('doc/config_values.md')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/config_values.md');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') != 'aa071e4d250e69e1181e83f47dab32a4610bc3ed') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/config_values.md');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/config_values.md', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/config_values.md');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') !== 'aa071e4d250e69e1181e83f47dab32a4610bc3ed') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') !== '7e24ada3a045f7900d8a7f1462b180b5c41d5a77') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/config_values.md');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/config_values.md');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/config_values.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/config_values.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_18();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') !== 'aa071e4d250e69e1181e83f47dab32a4610bc3ed') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/config_values.md');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('c3RlbSBhbmQvb3IgaXRzIG9iamVjdHMgKGlkZW50aWZpZWQgYnkgdGhlIGhhc2ggb2YgdGhlIG9iamVjdCBuYW1lKS4NCg0K'));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('doc/faq.md')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/faq.md');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('doc/faq.md')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/faq.md');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/faq.md') != 'cc09c1034a38b8c0edabf7a25afdfea715a96297') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/faq.md');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/faq.md', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/faq.md');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/faq.md') !== 'cc09c1034a38b8c0edabf7a25afdfea715a96297') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/faq.md') !== 'ef4ccaba9d4252dcf81bafb3ce247e8e0fd1d507') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/faq.md');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/faq.md');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/faq.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/faq.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/faq.md') !== 'cc09c1034a38b8c0edabf7a25afdfea715a96297') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/faq.md');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/website/features.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/website/features.html');
	writefile_20();
	if (!is_file('doc/website/features.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/website/features.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') != 'cf56996bd82deda6f2dd03855425b52e24e1f54e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/website/features.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/website/features.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/website/features.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== 'cf56996bd82deda6f2dd03855425b52e24e1f54e') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== '0dbafbad90c8f3a7d1a89030535c646d94cf2c80') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/website/features.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/website/features.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/website/features.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/website/features.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_20();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== 'cf56996bd82deda6f2dd03855425b52e24e1f54e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/website/features.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	writefile_29();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') != '58d8bbab0a81cb5a8e6f8e3e5ed5035f63973eab') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== '58d8bbab0a81cb5a8e6f8e3e5ed5035f63973eab') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== 'a7587e1368c7649e7e772a5a5fadac980c72f922') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_29();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== '58d8bbab0a81cb5a8e6f8e3e5ed5035f63973eab') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_30();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != 'cd3581f74c39d0622fa4f7d099dc820d46cfa2fa') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'cd3581f74c39d0622fa4f7d099dc820d46cfa2fa') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'e65a0e2c5677307118d3a54f66ed1a621900d15d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_30();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'cd3581f74c39d0622fa4f7d099dc820d46cfa2fa') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/WeidOidConverter.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/WeidOidConverter.js') != '663e064af5388604f33c7570d4a8e011b5f0a231') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/WeidOidConverter.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/WeidOidConverter.js', 0644)) {

	}

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/WeidOidConverter.js') !== '663e064af5388604f33c7570d4a8e011b5f0a231') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/WeidOidConverter.js') !== '9da7474f64bf1cecfbfad59f7080dfc40e50db38') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/WeidOidConverter.js');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/WeidOidConverter.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/WeidOidConverter.js') !== '663e064af5388604f33c7570d4a8e011b5f0a231') {

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html');
	writefile_37();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html') != '92fe636e010ed18ccde6ad6d143437924efa6f78') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html') !== '92fe636e010ed18ccde6ad6d143437924efa6f78') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html') !== '8fa04c6bae623e347d2920d93e1b7dd1b5c074b4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_37();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html') !== '92fe636e010ed18ccde6ad6d143437924efa6f78') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/tos.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql');
	writefile_38();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql') != '62240e44e03432cae6a655580532efa684076111') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql') !== '62240e44e03432cae6a655580532efa684076111') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql') !== '09685103a1552e549b948a7c01802b66befd858e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_38();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql') !== '62240e44e03432cae6a655580532efa684076111') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/example.sql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql');
	writefile_39();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql') != 'ef2d40823e5e6aa276ab40e5e2b4d01501fe8522') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql') !== 'ef2d40823e5e6aa276ab40e5e2b4d01501fe8522') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql') !== 'edacb888a5c35fe8ce6df48b5aac73987c553588') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_39();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql') !== 'ef2d40823e5e6aa276ab40e5e2b4d01501fe8522') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/example.sql');
		}
	}
}

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/example.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/example.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/example.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/example.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_40();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/example.sql') !== 'cb272d6dbd60baa71af54e6c8283e2b5c8826598') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/example.sql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql');
	writefile_41();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql') != '250dd500c4fc452511a761ddc5a97a184ee133fb') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql') !== '250dd500c4fc452511a761ddc5a97a184ee133fb') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql') !== 'c15fd76700bc7c2e0cc037514a59241ee8185556') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_41();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql') !== '250dd500c4fc452511a761ddc5a97a184ee133fb') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/example.sql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql');
	writefile_42();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql') != '26dc2ab749aa41ce0e28ed6ce103965905d5a1f6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql') !== '26dc2ab749aa41ce0e28ed6ce103965905d5a1f6') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql') !== '22665e6e1a90eba5d8991b9ac243e127ac029588') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_42();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql') !== '26dc2ab749aa41ce0e28ed6ce103965905d5a1f6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/example.sql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql');
	writefile_43();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql') != '90de3b1104580f040c6cb86b5f2cfcac3ab6f4b6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql') !== '90de3b1104580f040c6cb86b5f2cfcac3ab6f4b6') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql') !== '62596fdef41c5c67b6307837fcee750208c1f3cd') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_43();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql') !== '90de3b1104580f040c6cb86b5f2cfcac3ab6f4b6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/example.sql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql');
	writefile_44();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql') != '67ce5d2d1be5298b8867f3f644e3431dd1064ff9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql') !== '67ce5d2d1be5298b8867f3f644e3431dd1064ff9') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql') !== 'f85a55ec9652b9f8b138f76a4e45c0ce0880f8db') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_44();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql') !== '67ce5d2d1be5298b8867f3f644e3431dd1064ff9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/example.sql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	writefile_45();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') != '62e984e636cca064c44d869cd2747d4160a07572') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== '62e984e636cca064c44d869cd2747d4160a07572') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== '4182de38eb9b48b7b981da6c17fb8a8cdc4d22d3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_45();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== '62e984e636cca064c44d869cd2747d4160a07572') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_46();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') != 'fe7fa2781cd9ec522ca5b0cfb797f17d95731fc0') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'fe7fa2781cd9ec522ca5b0cfb797f17d95731fc0') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'cf5332d402832b2849c32403b26fa31a0ac29d26') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_46();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'fe7fa2781cd9ec522ca5b0cfb797f17d95731fc0') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
		}
	}

if (!is_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
	writefile_49();
	if (!is_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
	} else if (sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db') != '425e2b9b02c15bcac0636c9aacf67a14ca5faa97') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db') !== '425e2b9b02c15bcac0636c9aacf67a14ca5faa97') {
		if (@sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db') !== 'fd11337fe40bbd1b6d6d2ec13a7673308135c1e4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
			$tmp = pathinfo('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_49();
		if (@sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db') !== '425e2b9b02c15bcac0636c9aacf67a14ca5faa97') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/cacert.pem')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/cacert.pem');
	writefile_50();
	if (!is_file('vendor/cacert.pem')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/cacert.pem');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') != '20b1eff4a39c75e673c26b6f727547bb73c3dfa6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/cacert.pem');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/cacert.pem', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/cacert.pem');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') !== '20b1eff4a39c75e673c26b6f727547bb73c3dfa6') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') !== 'b0a93c92a2358cd0d9e9d202b6d60b69df9dab0b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/cacert.pem');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/cacert.pem');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/cacert.pem')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/cacert.pem', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_50();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') !== '20b1eff4a39c75e673c26b6f727547bb73c3dfa6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/cacert.pem');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.json');
	writefile_51();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') != '45d553b090374b6353d90139dfb21adb2fa4f550') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '45d553b090374b6353d90139dfb21adb2fa4f550') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== 'd639765a86a42dba48bd7c297ef0bd63858dbdd3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_51();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '45d553b090374b6353d90139dfb21adb2fa4f550') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.php');
	writefile_52();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') != 'e8abd2f45e34308444e500e1618be9d23e246877') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'e8abd2f45e34308444e500e1618be9d23e246877') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'fa92643ef9da9226b91cbb2b34257cc5a56b4600') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_52();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'e8abd2f45e34308444e500e1618be9d23e246877') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_59();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/danielmarschall/php_utils/oid_utils.inc.php');
